'''Hjallerup market''' is a market in [[Hjallerup]], about {{convert|20|km}} northeast of [[Aalborg]], Jutland, Denmark. It is one of the oldest and largest markets in Denmark and is the largest horse market in Europe.{{sfn|Olesen|2011|p=31}} Held for three days in the beginning of June, it annually attracts more than 200,000 people and 1200 horses.{{sfn|Olesen|2011|p=31}}

