{{Infobox road |country=SVK |type=R |route=2 |map=R2-SVK-map.svg |map_notes={{legend2|#008000|text=&lrm;|in operation}} {{legend2|#dc0000|text=&lrm;|under construction}} {{legend2|#9f32b2|text=&lrm;|in planning}} |e-road=[[Image:E58-SVK.svg|40px|E58]][[Image:E77-SVK.svg|40px|E77]][[Image:E571-SVK.svg|40px|E571]][[Image:E572-SVK.svg|40px|E572]] |length_km=50.5 |length_notes=Planned: {{convert|305|km|mi|abbr=on}} |terminus_a= SK/[[Czech Republic|CZ]] border |junction = |terminus_b= [[Košice]] ([[R4 expressway (Slovakia)|R4]]) |regions= |cities= }}
'''R2''' is an [[Highways in Slovakia|expressway]] in [[Slovakia]]. It starts from SK/[[Czech Republic|CZ]] border and leads to [[Trenčín]] ([[Motorway D1 (Slovakia)|D1]]) - [[Bánovce nad Bebravou]] - [[Prievidza]] - [[Žiar nad Hronom]] ([[R1 expressway (Slovakia)|R1]]/[[R3 expressway (Slovakia)|R3]]) - (shared section with R1/R3 until [[Zvolen]]) - [[Lučenec]] ([[R7 expressway (Slovakia)|R7]]) - [[Rimavská Sobota]] - [[Rožňava]], ending in [[Košice]] ([[R4 expressway (Slovakia)|R4]]).
As of 2006, from 358&nbsp;km (excluding the shared section) there were: * 50.5&nbsp;km in operation (21.5&nbsp;km as a two-lane road) * 3&nbsp;km under construction (two-lane road near [[Figa, Slovakia|Figa]]) * 305&nbsp;km planned
Note: Opened sections are currently signed as a national road [[I/50 (Slovakia)|50]].
